title: Educator.com - Geometry with Mary Pyo
description:
What do creating a videogame, piloting a spaceship, and building a skyscraper all have in common? They all utilize geometry. Geometry is Professor Mary Pyo's favorite subject and she brings her excitement when she focuses on student problem areas such as proofs. Mary begins each lesson with fundamental concepts and reinforces them with many examples. Additional topics include Inductive/Deductive Reasoning, Congruency, Proportions, and Transformational Geometry.
